name: Strength Tarot Card
description: The Strength card speaks to the inner strength and the human spirit's ability to overcome any obstacle. You have great stamina and persistence, balanced with underlying patience and inner calm. You are committed to what you need to do, and you go about it in a way that shows your composure and maturity. Your strength gives you the confidence to overcome any growing fears, challenges or doubts. Feel the fear and do it anyway! Created by Brian from Chicago @thebrau
